{"title":"多重背包问题 (改)","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":512,"tags":[],"operation":{"submit":"https://syzoj.com/problem/695#submit_code","submissions":"https://syzoj.com/submissions?problem_id=695","statistics":"https://syzoj.com/problem/695/statistics/fastest","testdata":"https://syzoj.com/problem/695/testdata","discussion":"https://syzoj.com/discussion/problem/695"},"statement":[{"title":"题目描述","type":"description","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"有 $N$ 件物品和一个容量是 $V$ 的背包。\r\n\r\n第 i 件物品体积是 $v_i$，价值是 $w_i$。\r\n\r\n求解将哪些物品装入背包，可使物品体积总和不超过背包容量，且价值总和最大。 输出最大价值。"},{"title":"输入格式","type":"input_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"第一行两个整数，$N$，$V$，用空格隔开，分别表示物品数和背包容积。\r\n\r\n接下来有 $N$ 行，每行两个整数 $v_i$ , $w_i$，用空格隔开，分别表示第 $i$ 种物品的体积、价值。"},{"title":"输出格式","type":"output_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"输出一个整数，表示最大价值。"},{"title":"样例","type":"example","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"INPUT\r\n```\r\n8 10\r\n2 3\r\n2 3\r\n2 3\r\n4 1\r\n4 2\r\n5 5\r\n3 2\r\n3 4\r\n```\r\nOUTPUT\r\n```\r\n13\r\n```"},{"title":"数据范围与提示","type":"limit_and_hint","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"- $0 \\lt N \\le 100,000$\r\n- $0 \\lt V \\le 10,000$\r\n- $0 \\lt v_i,w_i \\le10$"}]}